    "101208": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We've brought the perfumes, Mr. Zhongli!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Did we take too long? You were just staring up at the statue..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Oh, you're back. Don't worry, I haven't waited long."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Compared to the watch that Rex Lapis' statues have kept over Liyue, this was but a brief moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Haha, well, how can a person compete with a statue?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "That is true. Well, have you brought the perfumes?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Three sets and not one less!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Thank you both. Let us offer them up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Offer Golden House Maiden"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This is the first kind of perfume. Ms. Ying'er said that it's sweet as a dream, and it's liked by younger ladies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Offer Valley Weaver"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This is the second kind. It's got an elegant smell, and the daughters of high society love it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Offer Fate's Yearning"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The third kind has a gentle but lingering fragrance, something something like the dusk mist, and it's a favorite of mature ladies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh... what was that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Looks like Rex Lapis really likes this one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I guess the final answer is number three."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's the one older ladies like, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Does that mean that Rex Lapis is actually an older lady?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Haha, perhaps, perhaps."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Rex Lapis has taken on countless forms. Perhaps that really was one of them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What a shame, we only got to see the giant dragon form, and..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's hope the Qixing can catch the real killer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "We can leave that to the authorities. Let us focus on the fond farewell for Rex Lapis."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(What ulterior motives do Childe and the Qixing have...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Well, we do need to see the Exuvia...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, we've finished another step in our preparations. What's next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Next, I would like the two of you to help me borrow the Cleansing Bell."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Cleansing Bell?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "At present, a friend of mine named Madame Ping is the guardian of the Cleansing Bell. She lives near Yujing Terrace. If you ask her, she will know what to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sure, but... aren't you going to come with us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Ah, I have certain reasons why I cannot be there in person. Please do this for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Man, why's he got to be so secretive this time?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
