    "101401": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Madame Ping",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "All things must change..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How do you do?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Mm? Youngster, are you here to admire the flowers?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "But it's a shame. These Glaze Lilies have almost all wilted..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Are you alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "It's nothing, it's nothing. I just thought it a great shame that so many of these Glaze Lilies have wilted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What happened to them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Back in my day, people said that Glaze Lilies can read human hearts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "If they heard beautiful sounds like laughter and singing, they would also bloom joyfully."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "But if they heard too much wild gossip or slander, they would quickly wither away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...So that means these flowers feel what's happening in Liyue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Yes, the rumors of Rex Lapis' death are no small matter. They are everywhere."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Some say it was a Fatui plot. Others say that the Qixing made it all up, and still others think that That Which Lies in the Deep is breaking free."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "This harbor is like a mountain of dry tinder. One spark and the fire will consume us all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "...Well, I shall say no more. This old woman's grown too old and naggy... Did you have something to say, youngster?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'd like to borrow the Cleansing Bell."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Ah, that old trinket... I remember it being here with me, but I've grown old. I can't quite recall where it is exactly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "An old friend of mine used to wear it on his person, back when I was young..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "He saw me gazing at it often and gave it to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "But he told me then that if someone should come to borrow that bell, I should not be loath to part with it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'd like to borrow something from you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Borrow something? ...Oh, you've come to borrow the Cleansing Bell, yes?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Apart from that, I don't have anything of value that you youngsters might want."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "But it was not originally mine, either. That trinket used to belong to a friend of mine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "I was a vain beauty when I was young, and I would pester him for that bell all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "He could not dissuade me, and so he gave it to me. But he said that if someone should come to borrow it, I must not be loath to give it away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "It has been many years, and who knows how many times someone has come to borrow this bell."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Still, though I can't recall when it started, it's been a long time since anyone has come to borrow it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Ah, these old bones are so slow to look for things. I doubt you can wait that long..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can look for it ourselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's right granny. We'll follow you back home, and search for it ourselves!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And... Um, we can help with chores if you have any too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm a Knights of Favonius-certified lost property finder!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What a weird thing to be proud of..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Alright, children, there is no need to worry. I didn't place the bell very far away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? Do you live near here, granny? Whoa, but this is Yujing Terrace. It's gotta be expensive!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Haha, an old lady like me can't afford to buy a place in this city. See this ceramic teapot? My entire household is in here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...How does that work?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It contains your house keys?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The bell is all you own?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, that's rude!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...And even if it was like that, it must be a very expensive bell, right granny?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "In you go, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What!? There's no way Paimon would fit in there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And why do you need Paimon to go in, anyway? Can't you just lift the lid and look inside?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Madame Ping",
                    "T": "Hohoho, youngsters. I simply mean that the bell is somewhere inside this teapot, and you are quite welcome to borrow it — if you can find it."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
