    "101601": {
        "Desc": "Go to Third-Round Knockout",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Ah, you're here. There's no need to order, I've already done so."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "\"Third-Round Knockout\" is not for lightweights, like those taverns in Mondstadt. Here, the owner does not take such unorthodox orders as fruit juice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, does this mean I can order wine this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "I ordered some wine-fermented sweet rice balls for you, if that counts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I guess I should have expected this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "...If it is to your liking, dear customers, I shall continue the tale of Lady Ningguang's Jade Chamber."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, there's even a storyteller here! Great atmosphere!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "Besides fine wine, the excellent ambience is the reason why this place is so well-loved."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhongli",
                    "T": "But when I say ambience, I refer to a different sort from the one the Teyvat Travel Guide uses to judge other establishments."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "As you all know, high above the land of Liyue lies a pavilion in the clouds, a palace in the mist..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "What does it mean to have all-seeing eyes? This, my friends: Lady Ningguang's masterwork that bridges earth and sky."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "Imagine. The weather is clear, and you gaze down from the deck on the world below..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "Behold! The glorious sights of Liyue Harbor, stretching out far and wide!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "These are but scraps of paper, and yet they guide Lady Ningguang's hand — such is their value."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Tongue Tian",
                    "T": "Merely grasping one or two of them will surely gift you a fragment of her wisdom — enough to stay a step or two ahead of your peers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Tianquan Ningguang... feels like we're hearing this name a lot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Liyue locals talk about her, the Fatui hate her, she's most likely the one who hid the Exuvia, and we saw her at the Rite of Descension..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, Paimon wonders what sort of person she is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "At last, I have found you, you who returned from Jueyun Karst."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who's there!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon, we gotta go... !"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "Wait! I am not with the Millelith, nor am I here to claim your bounty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "However, I am an emissary of the Liyue Qixing. My name is Ganyu, secretary at the Yuehai Pavilion, and I have come specifically to meet you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Emissary?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Secretary?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "Well, in concrete terms, I am the corporate secretary for the Qixing. At the moment, I am serving as Lady Ningguang's special emissary."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ningguang sent you? We were literally just talking about her..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "My apologies, you who have returned from Jueyun Karst... I am duty-bound, and cannot extend my courtesy to you in full."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "But I have with me a letter from Lady Ningguang. She extends a formal invitation to you in her capacity as Tianquan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "She invites you to her palace in the sky."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "An official invitation...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "Lady Ningguang said this:"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "#\"Invite {F#her}{M#him} to come here.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "#\"I wish to meet {F#her}{M#him}.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ganyu",
                    "T": "\"At the Jade Chamber, together, we shall snip every one of these entwining dark threads.\""
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
